      "rawType": "F",
      "required": false,
      "helpText": "Intended as a means of defining functional groupings of physical locations. WING's may or may not equate to an extension or annex of a building, and/or a clinical specialty area (ex: surgical wing) of a hospital. Used in the Equipment Management Module. In sorting a Preventive Maintenance Worklist by LOCATION, the system will attempt to sort by WING rather than ROOM NUMBER. ",
      "fieldNumber_": 1
